Great depiction of the struggles of being a youth in the inner city of Chicago. I loved that it gave multiple sides of the story, so the viewer could definitely identify with at least one character. The duality of thought for the main characters to do what they knew to be right or do what they needed to do to survive really touches your heart and opens your mind.
